TPC_Energy_Upgrade defines:
	‚Ä¢	A concrete analytic energy (E_{\text{upgrade}}^{(A)}),
	‚Ä¢	A matching combinatorial energy (E_{\text{upgrade}}^{(C)}),
	‚Ä¢	A criterion under which these suffice to prove the Twin Prime Conjecture,
	‚Ä¢	And a precise architectural embedding into the PantheonOS proof stack:
	‚Ä¢	Millennium Guitar (F/E/S/R/C),
	‚Ä¢	PNT attractor class,
